### ========================================
### 36 - Dashboard & Me
### Current User Dashboard, Config,
### Clinical Dashboard, Assignments, Alerts
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### DASHBOARD CONTROLLER (/api/dashboard)
### ----------------------------------------

### Get current user dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### ME CONTROLLER
### ----------------------------------------

### Get dashboard config
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/dashboard-config
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get current user hospital
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/hospital
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get clinical dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/clinical-dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get my assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get critical alerts
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/critical-alerts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Acknowledge critical alert
POST {{baseUrl}}/me/critical-alerts/{{alertId}}/acknowledge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get inbox counts
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/inbox-counts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get roomed patients
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/roomed-patients
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get on-call status
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/on-call-status
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get active staff
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/staff/active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

